Reference Answer: True

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many puppies are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many puppies are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the puppy have its righthand ear erect and the other ear flopped forward?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
